Diamonds Homework

library(mosaic)
library(mosaicData)
library(tidyverse)
library(janitor)
library(GGally)

diamonds_3 <- 
  diamonds %>% 
  select(carat)

diamonds_3 %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = carat, y = price)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_smooth(method = "lm", se = FALSE)

diamonds_3 %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = carat, y = table)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_smooth(method = "lm", se = FALSE)
